sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant SCH as Scheduler
    participant MDS as MarketDataService
    participant EXT as Dis Saglayici
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant RED as Redis
    participant WS as WebSocket
    participant UI as Frontend
    participant EVT as EventPublisher

    SCH->>MDS: Periyodik guncelleme tetiklenir
    MDS->>EXT: Piyasa verisi cek
    EXT-->>MDS: Ham veri
    MDS->>MDS: Normalizasyon ve validasyon
    MDS->>DB: Kalici veri guncelle
    MDS->>RED: Cache yenile
    MDS->>WS: Anlik fiyat yayini
    WS-->>UI: topic/prices/*
    MDS->>EVT: Market data event yayinla
    Note over EVT: Topic = mintstack-market-data
